1
00:01:20,648 --> 00:01:25,437
"Love Beneath the Stars"
(Episode 5)

2
00:01:43,988 --> 00:01:45,582
Can someone explain what happened?

3
00:01:46,496 --> 00:01:52,086
Parents and sponsors have been calling
non-stop since this morning.

4
00:01:52,111 --> 00:01:55,573
I don't understand how this happened.

5
00:01:56,862 --> 00:02:00,793
Father, it's because of that video
going viral on social media.

6
00:02:01,068 --> 00:02:04,947
I tried to stop them but I was too late.

7
00:02:05,863 --> 00:02:09,045
Mr. Cruz! Mr. Armada! Stop that!

8
00:02:09,070 --> 00:02:11,113
Boys, stop recording!

9
00:02:11,316 --> 00:02:12,340
Stop that!

10
00:02:12,365 --> 00:02:14,067
This is a school activity.

11
00:02:14,092 --> 00:02:16,418
How dare you do something so scandalous!

12
00:02:16,443 --> 00:02:17,658
This is a Catholic school event

13
00:02:17,683 --> 00:02:19,864
