14
00:02:19,889 --> 00:02:21,407
Mr. Oyco, calm down.

15
00:02:21,432 --> 00:02:23,088
How can I calm down, Brother Mike?

16
00:02:23,113 --> 00:02:24,327
Didn't you see what they were doing

17
00:02:24,352 --> 00:02:25,550
in the middle of the dance floor?

18
00:02:26,478 --> 00:02:29,769
This is a disgrace to our institution.

19
00:02:29,794 --> 00:02:31,049
The students are going live!

20
00:02:31,074 --> 00:02:32,261
I said stop that!

21
00:02:32,582 --> 00:02:33,869
This is unacceptable.

22
00:02:33,894 --> 00:02:35,505
There's nothing wrong
with what they did.

23
00:02:35,530 --> 00:02:37,549
Do I really need to answer you,
Bro. Mike?

24
00:02:37,574 --> 00:02:40,927
Mr. Oyco, now is not the time
to get hysterical.

25
00:02:40,952 --> 00:02:42,550
The students are watching us.

26
00:02:43,011 --> 00:02:45,039
Dominic and Luke, step away first.

27
00:02:45,535 --> 00:02:47,208
Coach, please take Luke.

28
00:02:47,292 --> 00:02:48,626
Dominic, come with me first.

29
00:02:49,210 --> 00:02:52,063
Mr. Oyco, I suggest you
calm down the students.

30
00:02:52,088 --> 00:02:53,570
They're making a show out of this.

31
00:02:55,091 --> 00:02:57,539
This isn't over.

32
00:02:57,760 --> 00:03:02,789
We couldn't do anything
once it was posted on social media.

33
00:03:03,134 --> 00:03:04,929
It went viral.

34
00:03:05,382 --> 00:03:06,767
It had several shares.

35
00:03:06,792 --> 00:03:09,837
There are so many negative and
angry comments about our school.

36
00:03:10,566 --> 00:03:11,801
Everyone is wondering...

37
00:03:12,121 --> 00:03:18,106
why we allow such behavior
in an all-boys Catholic school.

38
00:03:18,949 --> 00:03:21,175
Those two boys must be expelled.

39
00:03:21,200 --> 00:03:23,959
Mr. Oyco, did you read all the comments?

40
00:03:23,984 --> 00:03:26,028
Or just the ones you wanted to read?

41
00:03:26,472 --> 00:03:30,731
Because there was a lot of
unexpected praise, too.

42
00:03:31,160 --> 00:03:33,281
Many commend us on being progressive.

43
00:03:33,306 --> 00:03:35,035
And how we, as a Catholic school,

44
00:03:35,060 --> 00:03:36,410
accepts all kinds of love.

45
00:03:36,744 --> 00:03:39,809
Shouldn't we be focusing
on those types of comments?

46
00:03:40,309 --> 00:03:42,885
And if you were to punish them,

47
00:03:42,910 --> 00:03:45,167
what were they in violation
of in the school handbook?

48
00:03:45,192 --> 00:03:47,963
Unbecoming of a gentleman.
Code of conduct.

49
00:03:47,988 --> 00:03:51,081
They should represent
what is right and just.

50
00:03:51,106 --> 00:03:53,683
So it's unbecoming of a gentleman to love?

51
00:03:53,708 --> 00:03:55,268
That's not my point, Bro. Mike.

52
00:03:55,293 --> 00:03:57,604
Do not twist the interpretation
of the handbook.

53
00:03:57,629 --> 00:03:59,964
Mr. Oyco, it's 2020.

54
00:03:59,989 --> 00:04:01,840
Let's go with the times.

55
00:04:02,033 --> 00:04:04,552
Even Pope Francis changed
his stand towards homosexuality.

56
00:04:04,577 --> 00:04:06,287
- You should, too.
- You dragged the Pope into this?

57
00:04:06,312 --> 00:04:07,824
Enough! Enough! Enough!

58
00:04:08,254 --> 00:04:09,839
Stop arguing!

59
00:04:11,023 --> 00:04:15,301
We should be focusing on a
solution to the problem at hand.

60
00:04:20,097 --> 00:04:22,910
You, Coach Mark, what do you
have to say about this?

61
00:04:24,238 --> 00:04:26,407
Well, Father Giboy...

62
00:04:26,572 --> 00:04:28,442
You're going viral on social media.

63
00:04:29,184 --> 00:04:31,128
Luke, there's no going back.

64
00:04:31,153 --> 00:04:33,449
The colleges will soon find out.

65
00:04:34,194 --> 00:04:36,530
This is the reality you chose.

66
00:04:37,371 --> 00:04:41,028
Coach, honestly,
I really don't care about that.

67
00:04:41,053 --> 00:04:43,392
Because all I can think about
right now is, Dominic.

68
00:04:43,417 --> 00:04:45,653
