71
00:04:54,652 --> 00:04:56,582
but Luke really loves Dominic.

72
00:04:57,371 --> 00:05:01,101
And I'm not sure if they
should be punished for it.

73
00:05:01,126 --> 00:05:03,379
But that wasn't the venue for that.

74
00:05:03,707 --> 00:05:04,799
It was a school event!

75
00:05:04,824 --> 00:05:05,988
Mr. Oyco, I know that.

76
00:05:06,278 --> 00:05:07,886
And I'm not defending their actions

77
00:05:07,911 --> 00:05:10,410
