78
00:05:11,370 --> 00:05:12,473
Okay, thank you.

79
00:05:12,894 --> 00:05:16,667
Now, what do you recommend we do?

80
00:05:16,692 --> 00:05:17,651
Expulsion.

81
00:05:17,676 --> 00:05:18,362
Warning.

82
00:05:18,387 --> 00:05:19,513
Suspension.

83
00:05:21,674 --> 00:05:23,012
Thank you.

84
00:05:25,156 --> 00:05:26,116
Okay.

85
00:05:26,716 --> 00:05:31,309
I will think about how to go about this.

86
00:05:32,918 --> 00:05:37,113
For now, Mr. Oyco, call them
in with their parents.

87
00:05:37,539 --> 00:05:40,334
Set a meeting with them
as soon as possible.

88
00:05:40,471 --> 00:05:44,832
The school should also
release a public statement.

89
00:05:55,263 --> 00:05:59,100
Dominic, this is totally unacceptable!

90
00:05:59,754 --> 00:06:03,466
