114
00:07:52,794 --> 00:07:54,262
I'm sorry, Dad.

115
00:08:03,037 --> 00:08:04,348
It's okay...

116
00:08:06,386 --> 00:08:07,551
It's okay.

117
00:08:19,535 --> 00:08:21,976
