on the video.

118
00:08:22,433 --> 00:08:26,787
"Those two guys are so cute."

119
00:08:26,812 --> 00:08:27,730
Ma.

120
00:08:28,858 --> 00:08:29,859
Why?

121
00:08:30,151 --> 00:08:32,556
I'm just trying to make you laugh.

122
00:08:32,581 --> 00:08:36,449
I don't see anything wrong with this video.

123
00:08:36,699 --> 00:08:40,321
People are over-reacting,
so small-minded.

124
00:08:40,346 --> 00:08:42,387
