125
00:08:44,910 --> 00:08:48,315
Well, there should be more like me.

126
00:08:48,340 --> 00:08:52,782
It wouldn't hurt to at least be kind.

127
00:08:54,176 --> 00:08:55,547
They're so frustrating.

128
00:08:55,572 --> 00:08:57,801
