137
00:09:50,871 --> 00:09:51,658
Bro, look. It's the fag.

138
00:09:51,683 --> 00:09:53,768
Bro, isn't that the guy from the video?

139
00:09:53,793 --> 00:09:55,378
Yeah, gross.

140
00:09:55,403 --> 00:09:57,405
