144
00:10:06,022 --> 00:10:07,064
Yuck.

145
00:10:07,679 --> 00:10:08,723
Idiots.

146
00:10:26,432 --> 00:10:27,558
May I sit?

147
00:10:30,141 --> 00:10:31,351
Why are you here?

148
00:10:33,365 --> 00:10:35,387
I saw you run in here.

149
00:10:36,298 --> 00:10:38,216
