166
00:11:47,581 --> 00:11:54,723
maybe because now I'm scared
because my parents are involved.

167
00:11:58,631 --> 00:12:01,092
You know how much I wanted
to make them proud.

168
00:12:02,384 --> 00:12:04,636
That's been my goal ever since.

169
00:12:06,735 --> 00:12:07,861
