170
00:12:10,521 --> 00:12:12,182
Worse than the time she caught us

171
00:12:12,207 --> 00:12:15,473
playing video games on a weekday.

172
00:12:16,902 --> 00:12:19,947
Shit. Monster Mom is back.

173
00:12:20,616 --> 00:12:22,441
I know, right.

174
00:12:25,650 --> 00:12:27,559
D, just always remember...

175
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:33,961
Many of us are ready to defend you.

176
00:12:35,102 --> 00:12:36,496
You are not alone.

177
00:12:38,624 --> 00:12:39,473
Okay?

178
00:12:42,224 --> 00:12:43,176
Thanks.

179
00:12:44,305 --> 00:12:45,996
