191
00:13:21,033 --> 00:13:22,535
Why are we meddling?

192
00:13:22,560 --> 00:13:24,904
You know Pim, you're something else.

193
00:13:24,929 --> 00:13:26,838
We all know how biased

194
00:13:26,863 --> 00:13:30,284
