Mr. Oyco is to people like us.

195
00:13:30,309 --> 00:13:33,771
Just hold a pink fan and we get punished.

196
00:13:34,012 --> 00:13:36,081
What more now with the viral video?

197
00:13:36,106 --> 00:13:39,004
If he had his way,
they'd both be expelled.

198
00:13:39,121 --> 00:13:41,940
- They don't deserve that.
- I get your point,

199
00:13:41,965 --> 00:13:43,689
but what they did is still wrong.

200
00:13:43,714 --> 00:13:44,381
How?

201
00:13:44,406 --> 00:13:46,503
It affected the whole school,

202
00:13:46,528 --> 00:13:48,385
and us being the
student body of this school

203
00:13:48,410 --> 00:13:50,174
should represent what is right

204
00:13:50,199 --> 00:13:51,971
for the majority of the students.

205
00:13:51,996 --> 00:13:53,474
Not just the LGBTQ+.

206
00:13:53,499 --> 00:13:55,837
You're really an ass!
So we're not part of that?

207
00:13:55,862 --> 00:13:57,280
Guys! Stop.

208
00:13:58,097 --> 00:13:59,057
That's enough.

209
00:14:00,231 --> 00:14:02,067
We should stop arguing.

210
00:14:03,113 --> 00:14:05,320
I understand they are partly at fault.

211
00:14:05,345 --> 00:14:08,015
And the school has the right
to give a sanction.

212
00:14:08,920 --> 00:14:11,297
Personally, I don't think
they're in the wrong.

213
00:14:11,646 --> 00:14:14,129
It's their right, their feelings.

214
00:14:14,535 --> 00:14:17,088
But the school got the backlash.

215
00:14:17,113 --> 00:14:19,083
But they didn't upload the video.

216
00:14:19,108 --> 00:14:20,226
I know, Timmy.

217
00:14:20,251 --> 00:14:23,699
That's why we need to ask
for a fair trial.

218
00:14:24,558 --> 00:14:26,309
They are the victims of this.

219
00:14:26,964 --> 00:14:29,758
That's why I believe we need
to make a stand about this.

220
00:14:30,738 --> 00:14:32,394
A fair stand that will tell the school

221
00:14:32,419 --> 00:14:35,215
that we are here to protect
the interest of everyone

222
00:14:36,872 --> 00:14:40,254
including the LGBTQ+ community.

223
00:14:41,768 --> 00:14:42,685
