245
00:15:46,400 --> 00:15:47,652
It's okay, Coach.

246
00:15:47,677 --> 00:15:50,263
If they don't want to pass that's fine.

247
00:15:52,089 --> 00:15:54,800
I'll just do my best if they
decide to pass the ball.

248
00:15:56,937 --> 00:15:57,778
Don't worry.

249
00:15:57,803 --> 00:16:00,356
