the rules of the handbook.

268
00:17:05,813 --> 00:17:07,832
But they didn't do anything wrong.

269
00:17:09,032 --> 00:17:11,848
I don't know why you can't see that.

270
00:17:12,084 --> 00:17:15,598
You teach us to be like Christ, right?

271
00:17:15,929 --> 00:17:18,331
To accept and love everyone.

272
00:17:19,387 --> 00:17:20,764
How is this any different?

273
00:17:20,789 --> 00:17:26,937
Mr. Dela Cruz, you are in no
position to tell us what to do.

274
00:17:27,258 --> 00:17:30,132
Actually Sir, I am, as the
president of the student council.

275
00:17:30,157 --> 00:17:31,657
And that is our stand.

276
00:17:33,071 --> 00:17:35,514
If the decision isn't fair,

277
00:17:35,539 --> 00:17:39,986
we are prepared to release
a statement against the school.

278
00:17:40,011 --> 00:17:42,008
- Are you threatening us?
- That's enough.

279
00:17:45,457 --> 00:17:46,750
Gio, calm down.

280
00:17:48,388 --> 00:17:52,102
I have not decided on anything
about the two boys.

281
00:17:53,883 --> 00:17:56,633
You are right and so is Mr. Oyco.

282
00:17:56,980 --> 00:17:59,453
It is not that simple

283
00:17:59,478 --> 00:18:01,836
because there are several
factors to consider.

284
00:18:03,949 --> 00:18:04,825
Okay?

285
00:18:05,412 --> 00:18:08,922
So please stop adding to the problem.

286
00:18:32,509 --> 00:18:35,024
(I know you need space, Dominic.)

287
00:18:35,049 --> 00:18:38,608
(Whatever happens tomorrow,
know that we'll survive.)

288
00:18:38,633 --> 00:18:41,665
(We can do this together, I love you.)

289
00:18:53,519 --> 00:18:54,438
Ben,

290
00:18:55,042 --> 00:18:56,794
don't go to work tomorrow.

291
00:18:57,204 --> 00:18:57,945
We need you there

292
00:18:57,970 --> 00:19:01,204
when we meet up with
the parents of that kid.

293
00:19:02,930 --> 00:19:04,579
Hon, do me a favor.

294
00:19:04,604 --> 00:19:06,673
Promise me you won't
make a scene tomorrow.

295
00:19:07,797 --> 00:19:09,173
Of course, I won't.

296
00:19:10,401 --> 00:19:13,375
But it doesn't mean that
I won't speak my mind.

297
00:19:14,774 --> 00:19:18,297
I still can't believe I'm being called
to the Headmaster's office.

298
00:19:18,518 --> 00:19:20,516
Never in my wildest dreams.

299
00:19:22,046 --> 00:19:23,305
Let's just eat.

300
00:19:25,883 --> 00:19:26,836
Rice?

301
00:19:27,160 --> 00:19:28,493
No, not today.

302
00:19:28,517 --> 00:19:29,907
Wow, no rice.

303
00:19:31,344 --> 00:19:33,263
Dominic, chicken?

304
00:19:33,918 --> 00:19:35,461
I'm okay.

305
00:19:44,486 --> 00:19:47,990
I'm sure you all know why
I called you in here today.

306
00:19:49,080 --> 00:19:52,219
The video of you two went viral.

307
00:19:54,244 --> 00:19:58,132
Though I don't see anything
wrong with two people in love.

308
00:19:58,157 --> 00:19:59,368
But what was wrong was...

309
00:19:59,731 --> 00:20:03,149
the time and place where it happened.

310
00:20:06,508 --> 00:20:08,974
Due to this, the school was affected.

311
00:20:08,999 --> 00:20:11,210
And because it's all over social media,

312
00:20:11,391 --> 00:20:14,539
we must release a statement.

313
00:20:15,336 --> 00:20:18,000
I asked the prefect of discipline

314
00:20:18,025 --> 00:20:21,688
what they think is a just
punishment for you.

315
00:20:23,043 --> 00:20:25,253
One said that you should be expelled.

316
00:20:26,196 --> 00:20:29,227
I believe that it is too extreme.

317
00:20:30,211 --> 00:20:31,747
Because your only fault

318
00:20:31,772 --> 00:20:35,336
was letting your emotions
run away with you.

319
00:20:44,123 --> 00:20:46,584
So what is your decision?

320
00:20:46,726 --> 00:20:49,297
You should thank the student council.

321
00:20:50,558 --> 00:20:52,137
Gio came to us yesterday

322
00:20:52,162 --> 00:20:54,998
to let us know where
the student body stands.

323
00:20:55,469 --> 00:20:59,232
I don't want to add any more
problems to the school,

324
00:20:59,257 --> 00:21:02,860
but they are right,

325
00:21:03,783 --> 00:21:06,911
you didn't violate anything
in the handbook.

326
00:21:07,547 --> 00:21:14,445
It doesn't say to punish
two people kissing.

327
00:21:14,470 --> 00:21:16,063
Because if there was,

328
00:21:16,844 --> 00:21:20,749
then I would have to punish
every boy and girl

329
00:21:20,774 --> 00:21:22,164
kissing during the Grad Ball.

330
00:21:22,556 --> 00:21:24,475
But your case is different

331
00:21:25,353 --> 00:21:29,733
because it went viral
and affected the school.

332
00:21:31,149 --> 00:21:35,608
And if I make the wrong decision,

333
00:21:35,633 --> 00:21:39,344
then the school will suffer more.

334
00:21:40,805 --> 00:21:45,352
So I made a decision that I think is fair.

335
00:21:47,529 --> 00:21:49,172
You will be suspended.

336
00:21:53,743 --> 00:21:55,205
Thank you, Father.

337
00:21:55,456 --> 00:21:56,789
But on one condition.

338
00:21:59,674 --> 00:22:01,196
You must break up.

339
00:22:05,985 --> 00:22:08,304
What does that have to do with this?

340
00:22:08,329 --> 00:22:09,450
Everything.

341
00:22:09,475 --> 00:22:11,204
Of course, they'll break up.

342
00:22:11,969 --> 00:22:14,444
They shouldn't have been
together in the first place.

343
00:22:14,469 --> 00:22:16,671
It is not our decision.

344
00:22:16,696 --> 00:22:17,829
And why not?

345
00:22:17,969 --> 00:22:21,296
We are the parents
and we know better.

346
00:22:21,321 --> 00:22:24,414
You know, that's why
your son is afraid of you.

347
00:22:24,742 --> 00:22:26,234
Because that's how you think.

348
00:22:26,621 --> 00:22:29,874
And that's why your son is messed up,

349
00:22:29,899 --> 00:22:31,717
because that's how you think.

350
00:22:31,742 --> 00:22:33,899
Hon, Mrs. Armada.

351
00:22:34,555 --> 00:22:36,922
This is not the place to argue.

352
00:22:37,391 --> 00:22:38,725
Sorry, Father Giboy.

353
00:22:39,413 --> 00:22:40,581
Are you both done?

354
00:22:41,254 --> 00:22:42,336
Sorry, Father.

355
00:22:42,610 --> 00:22:43,379
I'm sorry.

356
00:22:43,404 --> 00:22:46,164
There is only one reason why
I want you to break up.

357
00:22:47,032 --> 00:22:51,119
I don't want to add more
problems to the school.

358
00:22:52,081 --> 00:22:54,282
I am not against your relationship.

359
00:22:55,493 --> 00:23:03,368
But remember that St. Francis
is an institution of learning.

360
00:23:06,743 --> 00:23:10,100
I am here to honor what you choose,

361
00:23:10,125 --> 00:23:12,032
not what your parents choose.

362
00:23:12,175 --> 00:23:15,011
But Father, we are the parents.

363
00:23:15,493 --> 00:23:18,118
I think we should have a say
in this matter.

364
00:23:18,143 --> 00:23:20,687
Let them talk it out. We owe it to them.

365
00:23:21,083 --> 00:23:22,959
- I disagree.
- Honey,

366
00:23:23,546 --> 00:23:25,469
let's just step outside. Okay?

367
00:23:27,898 --> 00:23:29,733
Let's leave them to it.

368
00:23:30,716 --> 00:23:33,344
Let's head over to the other room.

369
00:23:34,456 --> 00:23:36,055
Let's give them time.

370
00:24:22,080 --> 00:24:22,955
I'm sorry.

371
00:24:24,523 --> 00:24:25,899
Everything is my fault.

372
00:24:26,607 --> 00:24:27,400
Please stop.

373
00:24:28,252 --> 00:24:29,461
Don't say that.

374
00:24:33,379 --> 00:24:35,256
Don't say sorry for loving me.

375
00:24:38,189 --> 00:24:38,875
No.

376
00:24:39,381 --> 00:24:40,507
That's not what I meant.

377
00:24:41,287 --> 00:24:42,997
I will never say sorry for that.

378
00:24:43,978 --> 00:24:46,258
I love you, Dominic. Always.

379
00:24:49,828 --> 00:24:51,454
I love you too, Luke.

380
00:24:55,999 --> 00:24:58,498
But this time,
love isn't going to be enough.

381
00:25:01,879 --> 00:25:04,149
Our future is on the line.

382
00:25:05,872 --> 00:25:10,252
What good is love if we can't graduate.

383
00:25:12,030 --> 00:25:14,196
I'm sure we can still talk to Fr. Giboy.

384
00:25:14,909 --> 00:25:16,781
We can make another compromise.

385
00:25:16,806 --> 00:25:18,183
That was it, Luke.

386
00:25:22,732 --> 00:25:24,552
We have to think about what's best

387
00:25:24,577 --> 00:25:26,250
not only for ourselves,

388
00:25:27,609 --> 00:25:29,594
but also for our families.

389
00:25:41,576 --> 00:25:42,954
I'm sorry, Luke.

390
00:25:45,897 --> 00:25:47,618
I'm not as brave as you.

391
00:26:10,500 --> 00:26:11,991
(Next Episode)
I have a favor to ask.

392
00:26:12,016 --> 00:26:13,514
I really want to talk to him.

393
00:26:13,539 --> 00:26:15,873
I think I know someone who can help you.

394
00:26:15,898 --> 00:26:17,342
Why are you doing this?

395
00:26:17,850 --> 00:26:19,899
Because I want you to be happy, Dominic.

396
00:26:20,696 --> 00:26:22,176
If you don't love me,

397
00:26:22,201 --> 00:26:25,163
please tell me
that you don't love me anymore

398
00:26:26,213 --> 00:26:27,954
so I can let you go.

399
00:26:28,060 --> 00:26:30,020
I'm not as brave as you, Luke.
